Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没骗人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 看看这个图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.50,0:02:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.90,0:02:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔 爱你啊 翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人又听不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟店员聊天时听说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那里的常客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次大家一起去吧 即使逃课也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.50,0:02:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 听说其他的偶像也经常去那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一些爱好者中很有名啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么用那种眼神看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做朋友的话找别人不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.90,0:02:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们修学旅行的小组成员决定了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好学习了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是努力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易如愿插班的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 诗织最近好像没怎么来玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近信越来越多了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是没有能商量的人呢 朋友之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.00,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女吗 来了吗 多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.00,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是考虑清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来想去 就只有这样做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是你死之后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样活着也是地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其在这里解开还不如在她面前解开的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打入地狱的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会是怎样的表情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真值得一看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个美容师好帅气 我真想去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笑容真恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织 今天放学后就要和你告别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在虽然有很多经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 插班生什么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.10,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi 到这里读中学吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是初中部的赤坂诗织 请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月开始就是同学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是涩谷南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧 这个乐队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没听过这个乐队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.20,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在这里 但是在那边很受欢迎哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌词也很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是英语的啊 看不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次翻译给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还把你当做好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到发生那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 诗织 弄得这么晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.60,0:07:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他科目就算了 只有英语很担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能一起回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.90,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤坂学的英语是叫皇后英语吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤坂家很大吧 真期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(444,278)\fs16}正在查询
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.45,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(444,278)\fs16}没有保存的邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(444,278)\fs16}没有保存的邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,190)\fs18}怎么不回消息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生体育课在体育馆集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育课啊　热得难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么想让折磨我吗 就像那时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是跟踪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.00,0:08:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔30分钟发邮件 绝对是跟踪狂没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为该怎么办好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老师说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师去和涩谷说说让她别这样做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下周日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些话要和你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我无话可说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织你误会了 我并不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有点疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜡迹可是洗不掉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织 我真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想对赤坂做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你就是那个跟踪狂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来惩办她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么跟踪狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织 至少你要相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.70,0:10:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了 不要再折磨我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再无视我也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织 我会让你受到惩罚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那样的眼神看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去保健室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备用这个咒杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到手指也是因为诅咒的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样想的话 那我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点去的话 要卖完了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡要续吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 能在收据上签字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加一句这事情决不外传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.00,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过我认为这东西不会派上用场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐就你付了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪狂 跟踪狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该诅咒的应该是南 你才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.10,0:14:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 灾难啊 轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 即使是丑时来 用的却不是五寸钉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的钉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}丑时咒还应该在人偶中加上被诅咒者的头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的孩子连用法都不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够可怜的啊 帮你拿掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,471)}怎么了 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,471)}不用回收了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,471)}暂时这样放着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过南那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑人偶被拿走了可怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所今天请假不去上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的指示吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.10,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止我复仇的指示吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个草人太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 应该不会就这样死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为先下手的是她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日程就这样安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体人员分成三人一组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 诗织 为什么到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经满员了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是之前不是说了一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们突然决定和上野同学一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事真对不起 所以还是做朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才对不起你啊 诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想把诗织送到地狱去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.60,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好过分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一有事就不当我是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.00,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的朋友只有南你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.70,0:18:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅之前的我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做回朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会在诗织那 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 南 这个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 已经没关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.90,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 和好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以外的结局啊 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看到最后吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌喜剧的结局吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒班里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个稻草人 不是普通的稻草人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用钉子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里的红线拉开 这样对方就会下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我解开的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 给你 解开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.00,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开啊解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.70,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话这 我死后也会去地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.30,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以 不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的朋友的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会帮我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说不是真正的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋…朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.20,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 诗织 我们是真正的朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南 南 哪里啊 哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.90,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.00,0:21:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你所希望的憎恨的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.10,0:21:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧 也许是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是诗织也有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.50,0:22:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为是朋友就为所欲为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也考虑下我的心情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位 和你一起的女孩哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.60,0:22:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我也会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.70,0:22:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边我们也做朋友吧 诗织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.60,0:22:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
